milestones.description: O'Brien has become the top wicket-taker for BMUDA in ODIs with 7 wickets, going past Hasan Durham's 4
Steven Outerbridge and Borden's 41-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 16 between Kwame Tucker and Gibbons
Clay Smith and Steven Outerbridge's 21-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 16 between Kwame Tucker and Mukuddem
Tucker and Mukuddem's 48-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 34 between Tucker and Romaine
Hasan Durham has broken the record for most catches (3) in ODIs for BMUDA, going past Lionel Cann's 2
Romaine has broken the record for most catches in an innings (2) in ODIs for BMUDA, going past Lionel Cann's 1
Kwame Tucker has broken the record for most dismissals (6) in ODIs for BMUDA, going past Dean Minors's 3
This is the lowest match aggregate (295) involving teams Bermuda & Canada in ODIs
Hasan Durham has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (4) for BMUDA, going past Dean Minors
Ashish Bagai has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (11) for CAN, going past John Davison
Kwame Tucker has broken the record for most dismissals in an innings (4) in ODIs for BMUDA, going past Kwame Tucker's 2

stories.title: Bermuda 'embarrass' Canada in opening game
stories.subTitle: Canada v Bermuda, 1st ODI, Toronto
stories.summary: In what will definitely rank as a big upset, and one which Andy Pick, the Canada coach termed was an 'embarrassment', Bermuda traipsed to a memorable six-wicket win in the opening one-dayer at Toronto
